cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with canonical logic programs and their comparison with propositional formulas.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as logic programming is a popular paradigm in AI and the paper discusses the representation of a problem in logic programming.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper discusses the complexity of representing a problem in different models of computation.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is another possibility as the paper discusses the complexity of representing the PARITY problem in different models of computation.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper deals with logic programming and its comparison with propositional formulas.
